6ad09f29124d906","tid":1322912,"uid":24834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 我係大埔人<br />\n尋晚收工11點由上水站坐到大埔站 發現有成卡大陸人 講唔知咩鄉下話 有大有細有大媽 呢個鐘數都覺得奇怪<br />\n一到大埔站 全撚部一齊落車 係月台有個大陸人示意佢地集合<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔撚妥 就係閘口外等佢地出閘 睇下咩情況<br />\n出閘後 佢地係閘口停左陣就往大埔墟方向走左 我就無再跟<br />\n<br />\n仆街 下次手足遇到同類狀況 要小心跟尾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKxvAnJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKxvAnJ.jpg&h=8fbf380e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNNSOKA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNNSOKA.png&h=dfeda820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衫黑短褲黑鞋戴帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸人做既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>反了反了<br />\n睇黎係上而受壓逼既同胞係上面無得發表聲音<br />\n只好係香港請求8國聯軍消滅共產黨 快分享出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0f04f09d1e02cb271db530f9c4b268470541435","tid":1322912,"uid":137629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47db1978f37d871c41c0430f9a763ec8e9ce578e","tid":1322912,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"仲以為4,50人會痴哂成條隧道, 原來1/5都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3fa80b44c006aea96245e595a74bce6d7f27e8","tid":1322912,"uid":5159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"機都唔識搾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bc3521f8849d4865718df876dd804c